        <div class="panel-title">
          <h2>Marketing automation was built<br>for a world that ended.</h2>
          <p class="panel-lede">Conversion's wedge is structural, not competitive. The window is open because Adobe is the slow-moving incumbent, the niche is real, and the timing is now.</p>
        </div>
