            <span class="label">Where Clay fits</span>
            <h3>Clay is not a competitor. Clay is the distribution channel.</h3>
            <p>Every modern B2B GTM operator lives in Clay. Clay is the enrichment and targeting layer. Conversion is the orchestration layer. Clay + Marketo is a duct tape operation. Clay + Conversion is an end state. Position Conversion as the orchestration layer for the Clay generation of GTM teams, and distribution happens for free.</p>
